From: Shaokun Zhang <zhangshaokun@hisilicon.com>
Date: Mon, 18 Feb 2019 21:05:01 +0800
Subject: x86/smpboot: Remove unused phys_id variable
Git-commit: f91fecc09e498529230b4d5053cb361619a0c42d
Patch-mainline: v5.1
References: git-commit

The 'phys_id' local variable became unused after commit

  ce4b1b16502b ("x86/smpboot: Initialize secondary CPU only if master CPU will wait for it").

Remove it.

